sequenceDiagram
    participant Y as Yannick / Session Manus
    participant SK as Skill (local)
    participant CA as Cache /tmp/yos-components
    participant GH as GitHub yos-components
    participant NT as Notion Registry

    Note over Y,NT: Scénario 1 — Premier appel (cache vide)
    
    Y->>SK: load_component("viz-mermaid-themed")
    SK->>CA: Check cache
    CA-->>SK: Cache MISS
    SK->>GH: git clone --sparse viz/mermaid-themed/
    GH-->>CA: Code v1.2.0
    CA-->>SK: Loaded
    SK-->>Y: Component ready
    Y->>Y: component.render(code, theme)

    Note over Y,NT: Scénario 2 — Appel suivant (cache chaud)
    
    Y->>SK: load_component("viz-mermaid-themed")
    SK->>CA: Check cache (TTL 24h)
    CA-->>SK: Cache HIT ✓
    SK-->>Y: Component ready (instant)
    Y->>Y: component.render(code, theme)

    Note over Y,NT: Scénario 3 — Publication nouveau composant
    
    Y->>SK: Développement local
    SK->>SK: Tests validés
    SK->>GH: git commit + tag "cog-mmm/v1.0.0"
    GH-->>GH: CI/CD tests
    SK->>NT: Update fiche composant
    NT-->>Y: ✅ Composant publié
    SK->>CA: Invalidate cache
